response.original_title: U-KISS JAPAN LIVE TOUR 2014 ~Memories~ RETURNS in BUDOKAN
response.overview: The final performance, filmed at the Budokan, of the 2014 U-KISS JAPAN LIVE TOUR 2014 has been released as a DVD and BluRay.  Several making-of videos and two new songs recorded for the first time are also included, and the first tour LIVE video in which new member Jun participated.  "One Call Away" and "Head Up High" that were unveiled for the first time on the day. In addition, five versions of "FEEL IT" are included; each version featuring each of your favorite members filmed from their own personal angle on stage.  A making-of video of the tour, that lasts about one hour, ends the release.
response.title: U-KISS JAPAN LIVE TOUR 2014 ~Memories~ RETURNS in BUDOKAN
